model.hed: Caitlyn Jenner Invites *AD* into Her Malibu, California, Home
model.dek: Caitlyn Jenner reveals her living room and bedroom makeover—designed by Lori Margolis—exclusively to *Architectural Digest*

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-02.jpg
items.caption: With stunning ocean and mountain views (and a 12-foot-long sofa from [Homenature](http://homenature.com/)), Caitlyn Jenner's monochromatic living room provides an ideal setting to entertain her extended network of family and friends. Ethereal curtains from [Diamond Foam & Fabric](http://www.diamondfoamandfabric.com/) and a Moroccan carpet from [Silk Road Oriental Rugs](http://www.silkroadorientalrug.com/) soften the modernist lines of the room. The lounge chairs covered in Tibetan lamb’s wool were custom sized for Jenner’s 6'2" frame by [Loft Thirteen,](http://loftthirteen.com/) and the chandelier is by [Lindsey Adelman.](http://www.lindseyadelman.com/)
items.credit: Photo: Rick Steil/Courtesy of Lori Margolis Interiors

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-01-before.jpg
items.caption: Jenner’s former living room, before a makeover by designer Lori Margolis.
items.credit: Photo: Courtesy of E!

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-03.jpg
items.caption: The living room is layered with soft, inviting textures; the lamp is by [Homenature](http://homenature.com/) and the tables are from [Graye.](http://www.graye-la.com/)
items.credit: Photo: Rick Steil/Courtesy of Lori Margolis Interiors

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-04.jpg
items.caption: The space has an organic, beachy vibe; the table is by [Homenature.](http://homenature.com/)
items.credit: Photo: Rick Steil/Courtesy of Lori Margolis Interiors

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-05.jpg
items.caption: The living room hearth is decorated with a geode and a vintage bust.
items.credit: Photo: Rick Steil/Courtesy of Lori Margolis Interiors

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-06.jpg
items.caption: A large Asian-style cabinet from [Shine by S.H.O](http://shinebysho.com/) is a dramatic focal point in the master bedroom.
items.credit: Photo: Rick Steil/Courtesy of Lori Margolis Interiors

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-07.jpg
items.caption: The bedroom’s tufted bed and quartz lamps are from [Homenature](http://homenature.com/), and the gold-accented nightstands are from [Shine by S.H.O](http://shinebysho.com/).
items.credit: Photo: Rick Steil/Courtesy of Lori Margolis Interiors

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-08.jpg
items.caption: Detail of the tufted headboard and a nightstand.
items.credit: Photo: Rick Steil/Courtesy of Lori Margolis Interiors

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-09.jpg
items.caption: Jenner is joined by (from left) her friend Candis Cayne, interior designer Lori Margolis, and design assistant Lawson Taylor.
items.credit: Photo: Rick Steil/Courtesy of Lori Margolis Interiors

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-10.jpg
items.caption: The master suite features a luxurious walk-in closet (not part of the makeover), where Jenner is shown with her stylist, Jennifer Rade.
items.credit: Photo: Courtesy of E!

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-11.jpg
items.caption: Jenner’s “glam room” (not part of the makeover), where she preps her hair and makeup.
items.credit: Photo: Courtesy of E!

items.title: dam-images-celebrity-homes-2015-caitlyn-jenner-caitlyn-jenner-home-malibu-california-12.jpg
items.caption: Jenner's modernist home has a dramatic setting, perched high in the hills of Malibu.
items.credit: Photo: Courtesy of E!
